            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Chop</strong> the potatoes roughly into small pieces</p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong>&nbsp;the ginger (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> 1-2 tbsp olive oil to a large pot with a matching lid over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong>&nbsp;hot, add the potatoes and cook for 2-3 min or until browned lightly on the outside</p>\r\n<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, slice the spring onions finely, discarding the root ends and keeping the whites and greens separated</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Coat</strong> the chicken with half of the harissa paste in a small bowl, then season generously with salt and pepper and mix well</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the chicken to the pot and cook for 2 min or until the chicken is brown and seared all over</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile, </strong>dissolve the stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span>&nbsp;in 500ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L]</span>&nbsp;boiled water</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the stock to the pot</p>\r\n<p><strong>Stir</strong> well&nbsp;and bring to a boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tip:</strong> scrape the bottom of the pot to prevent sticking!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/286.-step5-x1000.jpg",
