    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Give</strong> the chicken pot a good stir and add 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span>&nbsp;boiled water if it is too dry</p>\r\n<p><strong>Serve</strong> up the curry with a dollop of yoghurt and garnish with the sliced spring onion greens</p>\r\n<p><strong>Enjoy!</strong></p>",
